@startuml
title Diagramme de cas d'utilisation - Sprint 1
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle stickman

actor "Visiteur" as Visiteur
actor "Utilisateur" as Utilisateur
actor "Provider OAuth" as Provider_OAuth
actor "Service Email" as Service_Email

rectangle "Plateforme GOSPORT" {
  usecase "S'inscrire" as S_inscrire
  usecase "Valider formulaire" as Valider_formulaire
  usecase "Envoyer code verification" as Envoyer_code_verification
  usecase "Verifier email" as Verifier_email
  usecase "Se connecter" as Se_connecter
  usecase "Verifier mot de passe" as Verifier_mot_de_passe
  usecase "Connexion OAuth" as Connexion_OAuth
  usecase "Generer JWT" as Generer_JWT
  usecase "Reinitialiser mot de passe" as Reinitialiser_mot_de_passe
  usecase "Completer onboarding" as Completer_onboarding
  usecase "Acceder espace protege" as Acceder_espace_protege
}

Visiteur --> S_inscrire
Envoyer_code_verification --> Service_Email
Utilisateur --> Verifier_email
Utilisateur --> Se_connecter
Connexion_OAuth --> Provider_OAuth
Utilisateur --> Reinitialiser_mot_de_passe
Reinitialiser_mot_de_passe --> Service_Email
Utilisateur --> Completer_onboarding
Utilisateur --> Acceder_espace_protege

S_inscrire .> Valider_formulaire : <<include>>
S_inscrire .> Envoyer_code_verification : <<include>>
Verifier_email .> Valider_formulaire : <<include>>
Se_connecter .> Verifier_mot_de_passe : <<include>>
Se_connecter .> Generer_JWT : <<include>>
Acceder_espace_protege .> Generer_JWT : <<include>>
Reinitialiser_mot_de_passe .> Envoyer_code_verification : <<include>>
Se_connecter <. Connexion_OAuth : <<extend>>
Verifier_email <. Completer_onboarding : <<extend>>
Se_connecter <. Reinitialiser_mot_de_passe : <<extend>>
@enduml
